<http://example.org/req/852#PenaltyImpositionProcess> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000003>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000015>,
